##########################
# Setup webtools_retiree #
##########################

$prefix = wherever webtools installed (e.g., /usr/local/lib64/webtools)

For retiree do the following steps:

0) Copy sample configuration file.
   $ cd $prefix/config
   $ cp retiree_config.php.sample retiree_config.php
   $ vi retiree_config.php

1) Copy sample htaccess file to each webtool(s) directory.
   $ cd $prefix/html
   $ cp ../config/htaccess.sample retiree/.htaccess
   $ vi retiree/.htaccess

2) Done.
